  "raw_html": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"set-flags\">\n<span id=\"api-paddle-set-flags\"></span>\n<h1>set_flags<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#set-flags\" title=\"Permalink to this heading\"></a></h1>\n<dl class=\"py function\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\">\n<span class=\"sig-prename descclassname\"><span class=\"pre\">paddle.</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">set_flags</span></span>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span>\n<em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">flags</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">dict</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">str</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">,</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"pre\">bool</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">|</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"pre\">str</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">|</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"pre\">float</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span></em>\n<span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span>\n<span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">→</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></span>\n<a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/blob/release/3.3/python/paddle/base/framework.py#L133\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a>\n</dt>\n<dd>\n<p>This function sets the GFlags value in Paddle. For FLAGS please refer to <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../guides/flags/flags_en.html#en-guides-flags-flags\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">FLAGS</span></a></p>\n<dl class=\"field-list simple\">\n<dt class=\"field-odd\">\n           Parameters\n          </dt>\n<dd class=\"field-odd\">\n<p><strong>flags</strong> (<em>dict</em>) – A dict contains flags and its value.</p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p class=\"rubric\">Examples</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-python notranslate\">\n<div class=\"highlight\">\n<pre><span></span><span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">paddle</span>\n<span class=\"gp\">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class=\"n\">paddle</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">set_flags</span><span class=\"p\">({</span><span class=\"s1\">'FLAGS_eager_delete_tensor_gb'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"mf\">1.0</span><span class=\"p\">})</span>\n</pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n</div>"
